name: part_011
file: tmp_【#湊あくあ3周年記念 】あくあ色 3rd Anniversary Live【湊あくあ⧸ホロライブ】 [CtOkB0YQljY]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_011.mov

scenes.description: Minato Aqua performs her original song 'Kaisou Ressha' during her 3rd Anniversary Live.
Minato Aqua gives her closing remarks to the audience, announcing a membership-only 3D stream.
End card with a message of thanks to the viewers.

subtitles.original: ...世界へ
subtitles.english: ...to the world.

subtitles.original: 空白の路線図は今この手で
subtitles.english: The blank route map, now in my hands,

subtitles.original: 作り上げていく
subtitles.english: I'll keep building it.

subtitles.original: 海想列車 夢から醒めた
subtitles.english: Reminiscent train, I woke up from a dream.

subtitles.original: 懐かしくて
subtitles.english: It felt so nostalgic.

subtitles.original: 変わらない想いをそっと抱きしめた
subtitles.english: I softly embraced my unchanging feelings.

subtitles.original: 笑い合って 手を取り合って
subtitles.english: Laughing together, holding hands,

subtitles.original: 同じ時を過ごした
subtitles.english: we spent the same time together.

subtitles.original: 君と これからもずっと
subtitles.english: With you, from now on and forever.

subtitles.original: 海想列車 もう怖くはない
subtitles.english: Reminiscent train, I'm not afraid anymore.

subtitles.original: 無我夢中で
subtitles.english: So absorbed,

subtitles.original: 駆け抜けた日々は夢じゃないから
subtitles.english: the days we ran through aren't a dream.

subtitles.original: 正解なんて考えてみても
subtitles.english: Even if I try to think about the right answer,

subtitles.original: 分からないけど
subtitles.english: I don't know it, but

subtitles.original: 目の前に広がる
subtitles.english: spreading out before my eyes,

subtitles.original: この景色を見ていたい ああ
subtitles.english: I want to keep watching this scenery, ah.

subtitles.original: 君と一緒に
subtitles.english: Together with you,

subtitles.original: この景色を見ていたい
subtitles.english: I want to keep watching this scenery.

subtitles.original: メンバーシップでよかったら3D配信するので見に来てね！
subtitles.english: I'll be doing a 3D stream on membership, so please come watch if you'd like!

subtitles.original: 後ほどお会いしましょう！ということで
subtitles.english: I'll see you later! So,

subtitles.original: おつあくあでしたー！
subtitles.english: Otsuaqua!

subtitles.original: 4年目もよろしくねー！
subtitles.english: Please support me in my 4th year too!

subtitles.original: 見てくれてありがとう！ 4年目もよろしくね！
subtitles.english: Thanks for watching! Please support me in my 4th year too!
